<i>Well, my left hand's free</i>

02:26:11.137 --> 02:26:13.424
<i>Oh</i>

02:26:13.515 --> 02:26:15.757
<i>Well, my left hand's free</i>

02:26:15.850 --> 02:26:18.058
<i>Oh</i>

02:26:18.144 --> 02:26:20.431
<i>Well, my left hand's free</i>

02:26:20.522 --> 02:26:22.764
<i>Oh</i>

02:26:22.857 --> 02:26:24.723
<i>Well, my left hand's free</i>

02:26:24.818 --> 02:26:25.818
<i>Oh</i>

02:26:25.860 --> 02:26:28.193
<i>Oh, no</i>

02:26:30.657 --> 02:26:32.023
Who was it? Who hit you?

02:26:32.200 --> 02:26:33.361
Some guy.

02:26:33.535 --> 02:26:35.151
So itchy, man, God.

02:26:35.328 --> 02:26:36.535
What's "some guy's" name?

02:26:36.705 --> 02:26:38.196
Uh, Steve.

02:26:38.373 --> 02:26:40.365
Steve? From 12-C?

02:26:40.542 --> 02:26:42.408
- With the overbite?
- No, no, no.

02:26:42.711 --> 02:26:44.327
You don't know him. He's from Brooklyn.

02:26:47.257 --> 02:26:48.257
Ouch.

02:26:48.383 --> 02:26:49.383
Well...

02:26:50.176 --> 02:26:51.917
I hope you got a few good licks in.

02:26:52.178 --> 02:26:54.420
Yeah, I got quite a few in, actually.

02:26:55.181 --> 02:26:58.219
His friend was huge. Like huge.

02:27:00.729 --> 02:27:03.062
That's way better. Thank you.

02:27:03.231 --> 02:27:05.223
Okay, tough guy.

02:27:07.902 --> 02:27:10.019
Love you, May.
Hey, can you shut the door?
